latestIgtvVideos.title: Roberto Cavalli FALL WINTER 2023-24
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
She’s wild.
 
For Fall Winter 23/24 @faustopuglisi designs for a Cavalli woman who is free in spirit, sensual and wild at heart.
 
A collection with luxurious fake furs, prints, denim and devoré all inspired by a balanced mix of muses such as Milicent Rogers and Georgia O’ Keefe. Join us on a trip to the American Southwest via a warm and earthy palette with notes of pink.

latestIgtvVideos.title: #RobertoCavalli SS23
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
A game of opposites sets the tone of the #RobertoCavalliSS23 Fashion Show by @faustopuglisi.
Prim and prissy with her chunky headband, perched on high heels or in pointy flats, the #RobertoCavalli heroine looks like a good girl, but she is definitely not.

The signature elements of the Cavalli world, prints and jacquard motifs with a feline appeal, blend into a constellation of British inspiration, for a cool and metropolitan look - the #RobertoCavalli  Pre-Fall Collection 2022 by @faustopuglisi available now.
Discover the Roberto Cavalli Pre-Fall 2022 Collection by @faustopuglisi available now.

Soft shapes and vintage notes, with bold, sharp, rock ‘n’ roll spirit - during Milan Design Week 2022, Roberto Cavalli is presenting a preview of the new Home collection in its Montenapoleone boutique.
Queen of Cavalli Chairs: 20 limited-edition pieces from Roberto Cavalli Home Interiors, designed by @faustopuglisi.
Wild animals motifs and timeless leopard prints - Roberto Cavalli Women’s Resort Collection 2023 by @faustopuglisi.
Modern essentials delivering a multifaceted collection - Roberto Cavalli Resort 2023 by @faustopuglisi.
Elegance, unapologetic femininity and eclectic fun - the Roberto Cavalli Resort Women’s Collection 2023 by @faustopuglisi.

A night to remember. 

The #RobertoCavalli Fall/Winter 2022-23 by @faustopuglisi Womenswear Fashion Show was a vision for the future of womenswear combining street urban aesthetic with timeless Italian design. 
In case you missed the live show last night, watch the full show here.
